title: For Sale/Trade:  Lyman 49th Edition Reloading Handbook (Hardcover)
postcontent: Lyman's 49th Edition Reloading Handbook is the most popular rifle and pistol reloading manual. The 49th Edition covers all popular rifle calibers.Used with some highlighting but in excellent condition otherwise. I like to keep my reference manuals clean.- World's most popular loading manual- Incorporates data from all major component manufactuerers- Loading data on all the newest catrtridges- Powders from Alliant, Hodgdon, IMR, Vihta Vuori, and others- Articles by well known reloading authoritiesThe Lyman manual lists the specific projectiles used for each cartridge, including the BC (ballistic coefficient) and SD (sectional density) for those projectiles. Also provided is the chamber(s), barrel twist rate(s), barrel length(s), and firearm platform(s) that the projectiles are fired from. Each set of data for a specific bullet contains what Lyman found to be the most accurate loading, which is in bold print. Compressed charges are indicated with a "+" after the charge weight. There is even some data for lead projectiles included at the end of the data for each caliber. One issue I have with the data is that Lyman often switches from PSI to CUP when listing pressures. Will ship via USPS Media Mail for actual cost.
